      "start_offset": 53227,
      "end_offset": 64684,
      "page_number": 13,
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "section_id": "3.4.2",
          "heading": "Recommendation 3.4.2: We suggest that in children with CKD, 24-hour mean arterial pressure (MAP) by ambulatory blood pressure monitoring (ABPM) should be lowered to \u226450th percentile for age, sex, and height (2C).",
