          "end_offset": 64684,
          "page_number": 13,
          "block_type": "heading",
          "level": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "section_id": "3.7.1",
              "heading": "Recommendation 3.7.1: We recommend treating patients with type 2 diabetes (T2D), CKD, and an eGFR \u226520 mL/min/1.73m\u00b2 with an SGLT2i (1A).",
              "start_offset": 61261,
              "end_offset": 64684,
