        {
          "section_id": "3.15.1.5",
          "heading": "Practice Point 3.15.1.5: Consider a plant\\-based \u201cMediter\\- ranean\\-style\u201d diet in addition to lipid\\-modifying therapy to reduce cardiovascular risk.",
